entry.title: Hello
entry.summary: A member of the Lightning-dev mailing list, Cezary Dziemian, posted a message asking why he had not received any emails since joining the list a week ago. The post was made on October 8th, and there had been no discussion on the list since September 19th. The mailing list has an archive available for users to review previous discussions. The Lightning-dev mailing list is hosted by the Linux Foundation.
